These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, salsa, electronic, disco
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of electronic and the fan of disco##2
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | disco | salsa | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, 7up, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk | water | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, goat, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | horse | hamster | goat | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
